      </p></div><div><p><a title="Platforms > Nintendo [21,875 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo">Nintendo</a> has released a new commercial for <a title="Platforms > Switch 2 [110 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch-2">Switch 2</a> dubbed “Now You’re Playing Together,” which features actor Paul Rudd and is a callback to a 1991 <a title="Platforms > SNES" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/snes">Super Nintendo Entertainment System</a> commercial that also featured Rudd. <span id="more-959763"></span></p><p>The company also uploaded the original Super Nintendo Entertainment commercial as a direct comparison.</p><p>Switch 2 is due out on June 5. Pre-orders will open in the United States and Canada <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/04/switch-2-pre-orders-begin-april-24-in-the-us-and-canada-pricing-unchanged">on April 24</a>.</p><p>Watch the commercials below.</p><h2><span>“Now You’re Playing Together” featuring Paul Rudd</span></h2><p><iframe title="Now You're Playing Together ft. Paul Rudd – Nintendo Switch 2" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/3uGXvdbL1ys?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><!-- AD: content -->
